('Great minds discuss ideas; average minds discuss events; small minds discuss people.', '伟大的心灵讨论思想；平庸的心灵讨论事件；渺小的心灵讨论人。', 'Eleanor Roosevelt', '埃莉诺·罗斯福', 'advanced', 'motivational'),
